				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-card-foreground">Service Three</h3>
				<p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">Detailed description of the third service offering and how it benefits clients.</p>
				<a href="/services/service-three" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 font-medium">Learn more →</a>
